Definition.Document:
Polytropic Exponent

Polytropic exponent can be determined from 

 

1. Use the External Calculation function in Formula to determine the densities at the suction and discharge based on its pressures and temperatures (python script does the calculation) (workstep - suction)

  • 1st stage comp suction Density
  • 1st stage comp discharge Density

Note: デモでは Methane を想定しています。

2. Once the densities are calculated, the isentropic exponent can be calculated as well.  (workstep)

  • Polytropic exponent

1. pythonスクリプトを使用し、圧力と温度から吸込と吐出の密度を求めます。
 to determine the densities at the suction and discharge based on its pressures and temperatures (python script does the calculation). (workstep - suction)
